        <Parent_String>frames by location or context [300223179], frames (protective furnishings) [300189814], furnishings by form or function [300037342], furnishings (works) [300037336], Furnishings (hierarchy name) [300037335], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
